        "synopsis": {
            "value": "On Jeju Island, Won Mi-Ho (Lee Da-Hee) feels despair due to the deaths of people around her. She vows not to lose anyone else and undergoes training from Geum Baek-Joo (Ko Du-Shim) to regain the powers she once had as Wonjeong. In ancient times, Wonjeong was destined to save her people on Jeju Island by creating a barrier from the lust demons that rampaged over the island. Two boys, Van and Gungtan were raised nearby solely to kill the lust demons, but they escaped.\n\nNow, Van (Kim Nam-Gil) and Priest Johan (Cha Eun-Woo) watch from afar as Won Mi-Ho tries to awaken the energy that she was once held. Meanwhile, Gungtan (Sung Joon) lurks in the background filled with fear and rage. He begins his quest to throw the world into chaos and darkness.",
